eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A FIRE WARNING FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Sheboygan, WI; AT 01:02 PM ON NOV 14, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 03:09 PM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: Due to a gas line being struck, emergency crews are asking for an evacuation of 3 miles of Trio Lane. Those within in the evacuation area are being asked to meet at Cascade Fire Department. If you live within three miles of Trio Lane please evacuate the area.
